    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Business Email Management - Outlook Edition\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Outlook Trigger polls every minute for unread emails\n2. AI classifies via OpenRouter (gpt-5.1)\n3. Switch node routes by department\n4. Outlook categories applied for inbox organization\n5. Urgent emails flagged with extra category\n6. Draft replies created for review (never auto-sent)\n7. Every email logged to Google Sheets\n8. Sales leads tracked + Outlook calendar follow-up\n\n**Credentials Needed:**\n- Outlook: Microsoft Outlook OAuth2 (Azure App)\n- Sheets: Google Sheets AVM Tutorial\n- AI: OpenRouter account\n\n**Setup Required:**\n1. Azure App Registration (see plan)\n2. Create 7 Outlook categories\n3. Connect credentials in n8n",
        "height": 600,
        "width": 380
